  "keyFeatures": [
    "Low-bit quantization (INT4/INT5/INT8/FP4/FP6/FP8) for LLM acceleration on Intel hardware",
    "Support for 70+ LLMs including LLaMA, Mistral, DeepSeek, Qwen, ChatGLM, Phi, Gemma, and more",
    "Seamless integration with Ollama, llama.cpp, vLLM, HuggingFace Transformers, LangChain, LlamaIndex",
    "GPU inference and QLoRA finetuning on Intel Arc, Flex, Max, and iGPU",
    "NPU acceleration on Intel Core Ultra processors (Windows)",
    "Pipeline parallel inference across multiple Intel GPUs",
    "One-line code change for HuggingFace Transformers-based applications",
    "Docker and portable zip deployment options",
    "FlashMoE support for running 671B parameter MoE models on 1-2 Arc GPUs"
  ],
